Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ca-certificates,
 curl | wget,
 tar
Description: Luthéal Piano Cimbalom SFZ instrument
 SFZ instrument mapping of the Luthéal piano in cimbalom (all stops) registration.
 .
 Sample FLACs are downloaded on first install from the project's GitHub release
 assets (~1 GiB). The SFZ is installed to /usr/share/sfz/pianos/lutheal/ for
 use with SFZ-compatible samplers (sfizz, Sforzando, etc.).
